rComments: Hard grader, tests were difficult to study for as was paying attention in class

For the amount of work that's required for this class, it should have been worth advanced hours. Sure, you don't have to keep up with the reading, but if you don't there's no way you're going to pass the class on just the handouts. The final is worth 50% of your grade. DO NOT TAKE THIS CLASS.
